title: [1508521049] Roast Pumpkin Soup (Part 2) - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay prepares his pumpkin soup - perfect for warming you up on a cold day. Subscribe for weekly videos. 

The most delicious Christmas recipes, cooked up by the world's greatest chef at home, Gordon Ramsay's Ultimate Christmas will teach you everything you need to know to cook up the perfect Christmas.

The official YouTube channel of Gordon Ramsay, with exclusive clips from a selection shows including Cookalong Live, Gordon's Great Escape and more.

To find out more about Gordon Ramsay visit:
